<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto my-12 px-4 pb-24 font-sans text-stone-800">
  <div class="animate-fade-in-up text-center mb-16" style="animation-delay: 0.1s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-black bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl py-4 px-8 tracking-widest mt-4 inline-block">
      自炊save の使い方
    </h1>
    <p class="text-stone-400 font-medium mt-2">賢く自炊して、お得に楽しもう！</p>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-24">
    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10" 
        style="animation-delay: 0.3s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide_1.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">1</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">コンビニ価格と比較する</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          投稿画面で、作りたい料理に近いコンビニ商品やお弁当を選びましょう。<br>自動的に価格が表示され、自炊との差額がリアルタイムで計算されます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 0.5s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide_2.jpg", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">2</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4 text-right md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">材料とグラムを入れるだけ</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          使った材料と重さを入力すると、自動でコストを算出。「目安表」を使えば、計りがなくてもざっくり計算できます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 0.7s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/new_guide.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">3</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">自炊を記録する</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          自炊したレシピの「作る」ボタンをクリックして、節約金額と自炊回数を記録しましょう。<br><br>
          レシピの詳細画面にあるコピーボタンを使えば、自分なりのアレンジレシピも簡単に作れます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 0.9s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/step-new-guide.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">4</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4 text-right md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">頑張りを共有</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          プロフィール画面では、自炊記録の他に様々な機能が使えます。<br>
          頑張りを誰かと共有したいときは、「Xシェア機能」で今月のあなたの頑張りをシェアしましょう！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 1.1s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide-step-4.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">5</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">目標を立てる</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          プロフィール画面では、「作る」ボタンを押したレシピの節約額が集計されます。<br><br>
          グラフの表示で、「これだけお得になった！」「頑張って自炊できている！」というのが一目でわかるので、楽しく自炊を続けられます！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-fade-in-up flex flex-col md:flex-row-reverse items-center gap-10"
        style="animation-delay: 1.3s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
        <div class="relative bg-orange-100 rounded-[3rem] p-4 shadow-inner">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-[2.5rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl border-4 border-white aspect-[9/16] flex items-center justify-center text-stone-300">
            <%= image_tag "guide/guide-step-5.png", class: "w-full h-full object-cover" %>
          </div>
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -right-4 w-12 h-12 bg-orange-500 text-white rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-black shadow-lg">6</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/2 space-y-4 text-right md:text-left">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800">LINE通知で習慣化</h2>
        <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed font-medium">
          LINE連携をすれば、あなたが決めた日時に通知が届きます。<br>
          自分のペースに合わせて無理なく自炊の習慣化を手助けします！
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr class="border-t-2 border-dashed border-stone-300 mt-20">

  <div class="max-w-md mx-auto mt-20 px-6 space-y-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-stone-800 mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
      快適に使うための設定
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-8 relative before:absolute before:left-4 before:top-2 before:bottom-2 before:w-0.5 before:bg-stone-100">
      
      <div class="relative pl-10">
        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <span class="text-orange-500 font-black text-sm">1</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-stone-800">ブラウザでログイン</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-1">
          SafariやChromeで <code class="bg-stone-100 px-1 rounded">jisui-save.com</code> を開き、まずはログインを完了させます。
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-10">
        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <span class="text-orange-500 font-black text-sm">2</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-stone-800">ホーム画面に追加</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-1">
          ログインした状態のまま、ブラウザのメニューから「ホーム画面に追加」を選択します。
        </p>
        
      </div>

      <div class="relative pl-10">
        <div class="absolute left-0 w-8 h-8 bg-white border-2 border-orange-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center z-10">
          <span class="text-orange-500 font-black text-sm">3</span>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-black text-stone-800">準備完了！</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-stone-500 mt-1">
          次からはアイコンをタップするだけで、すぐに自炊記録を始められます。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 p-5 bg-stone-50 rounded-3xl border border-stone-200">
      <h4 class="text-xs font-black text-stone-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">⚠️ 注意事項</h4>
      <ul class="text-xs text-stone-500 space-y-2 font-bold leading-relaxed">
        <li>・LINEログイン時、初回のみメアドやQR認証が必要になる場合があります。</li>
        <li>・うまく動かない場合は、再度「通常のブラウザ」からお試しください。</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="animate-fade-in-up mt-24 text-center" style="animation-delay: 1.5s; opacity: 0; animation-fill-mode: forwards;">
    <%= link_to "さっそく作ってみる", new_recipe_path, class: "inline-block bg-orange-500 hover:bg-orange-600 text-white font-black px-12 py-5 rounded-[2rem] shadow-xl shadow-orange-200 transition-all active:scale-95 text-xl" %>
  </div>
</div>